description: This big pink truck with its dancing donut decor is where all of Baltimore delights in Deddle’s award-winning mini donuts & buttermilk fried chicken strips. You, too, are warmly invited to stop by and top these fresh hot fried minis with a wide range of tastiness; bacon crumbles, strawberry sauce, and cinnamon sugar, to name a few. And along with Deddle’s signature sweet and friendly smile, the delicious golden fried chicken perfectly completes this quite wonderful treat.
name: Deddle's Mini Donuts & Chicken
